<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">感谢大家的邀请。<br><br>自从回答了这个问题以后，我是吃一堑长一智。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/8f7afc793ec5ef484b91a445d3c8faff_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="341" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="620" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/8f7afc793ec5ef484b91a445d3c8faff_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="341" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="620" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/8f7afc793ec5ef484b91a445d3c8faff_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/8f7afc793ec5ef484b91a445d3c8faff_b.jpg"><a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/26452085/answer/32823630" class="internal">男朋友问他和张国荣谁更帅，应该怎么回答？ - Kaiser 的回答</a><br><br>你先告诉我你是男的女的。<br><br>————————————————————<br>嗯，好，我知道了。<br><br>我要给你提供一个方案，这个方案保证好使，反正对我是好使的。<br>总结起来一个字，就是，买。<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/9a709daec85bda9bc5f90776141cbbe2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1340" data-rawheight="646" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1340" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/9a709daec85bda9bc5f90776141cbbe2_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1340" data-rawheight="646" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1340" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/9a709daec85bda9bc5f90776141cbbe2_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/9a709daec85bda9bc5f90776141cbbe2_b.jpg">


